description.text: Excellent Investment Opportunity in Prime Hancock Park Wilshire in Los Angeles! Built in 1989, this well-maintained 9-unit apartment building features nicely renovated units and exterior, offering a true turnkey investment. No Rent Control of RSO, allowing for maximum rental flexibility and future upside. Located in a high-demand rental area with consistent occupancy, this property is ideal for investors seeking stable cash flow with long-term appreciation potential.
